# NYC Subway Ridership

## Intro
In this project, I looked at NYC Subway data and figured out if more people ride the subway when it was raining versus when it was not raining. I also wrangled the NYC subway data, used statistical methods and data visualization to draw an interesting conclusion about the subway dataset.
